html
  head
    title URL Shortener Microservice | FreeCodeCamp
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous")
  body
    .container
        .page-header
            h1 URL Shortener Microservice #[small FreeCodeCamp API Projects]
        .content
            p
                |This is an implementation of FreeCodeCamp's 
                a(href="https://www.freecodecamp.com/challenges/url-shortener-microservice") URL Shortener API project
                |.
            h3 Example usage:
            code= siteurl+'/new/https://www.google.com'
            br
            code= siteurl+'/new/http://foo.com:80'
            h3 Example creation output:
            code
                |{ "original_url":"http://foo.com:80", "short_url":"#{siteurl}/4obu0A"}
            h3 Usage
            code #{siteurl}/4nHX1I
            h3 Will redirect to
            code https://www.google.com